Package tech.tablesaw.selection

Interface Selection

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Filter, it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints.IntIterable, Iterable<Integer>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BitmapBackedSelection

    public interface Selection
extends it.unimi.dsi.fastutil.ints.IntIterable, Filter
    A selection maintains an ordered set of ints that can be used to eval rows from a table or column
